---
// src/pages/community/feeding-scheme.astro
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout
  title="Two Weeks. Every Child Fed."
  description="In 2024, eKoneni Lounge ran a two-week feeding scheme for children in Mdantsane — no conditions, no fanfare. Just meals on the table every day."
>
 
  <!-- Back link -->
  <div class="section-dark pt-28 sm:pt-32 pb-0 px-5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/community" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-body text-amber-400/70 text-sm hover:text-amber-400 transition-colors duration-200 mb-8">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18"/>
        </svg>
        Back to Community
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Story hero -->
  <div class="section-dark pb-16 px-5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-400/10 border border-amber-400/20 font-body text-amber-400 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
        Feeding Scheme · 2024
      </span>
      <h1 class="section-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white leading-tight mb-8">
        Two Weeks.<br/>
        <span class="text-amber-400">Every Child Fed.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        No press release. No sponsorship deal. No conditions.
        Just eKoneni showing up for the children of Mdantsane, every day, for two weeks straight.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Cover image -->
  <div class="section-dark pb-0 px-5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[320px] sm:min-h-[440px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10 mb-3">
        <!-- Swap for real image: <img src="/images/community/feeding-scheme-cover.jpg" alt="..." class="w-full h-full object-cover"> -->
        <div class="text-center p-8">
          <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-amber-400/20 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
          </svg>
          <p class="font-body text-amber-400/30 text-sm">Replace with cover photo from Facebook</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-xs text-center mb-16">eKoneni Lounge · Mdantsane, 2024</p>
    </div>
  </div>
 
  <!-- Story body -->
  <section class="section-mid py-16 px-5">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
 
      <!-- Narrative -->
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-16">
        <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Hunger doesn't announce itself. It's quiet, and it's often invisible — especially when it's children
          who carry it. In 2024, eKoneni Lounge decided to do something about it, not as a marketing campaign,
          but as neighbours.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          For two full weeks, the team ran a feeding scheme for children in Mdantsane.
          Every day. A proper meal. No hoops to jump through, no forms to fill in.
          If you were a child in the neighbourhood, you were fed. Simple as that.
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          This is what eKoneni means when it says it is more than a lounge.
          The dancefloor is where the community celebrates. This is where it holds each other up.
          <span class="text-amber-200/80">Sibanakekelene — we look after each other.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
 
      <!-- Stats strip -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6 mb-16 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl border border-amber-400/10 bg-amber-400/5">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-400">14</p>
          <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1 tracking-wide uppercase">Days running</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center border-x border-amber-400/10">
          <p class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-400">0</p>
          <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1 tracking-wide uppercase">Conditions</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-amber-400">∞</p>
          <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-xs mt-1 tracking-wide uppercase">Community love</p>
        </div>
      </div>
 
      <!-- Photo grid -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white mb-8">
          On the <span class="text-amber-400">Ground</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <!-- Photo slots — uncomment and update src when photos are available -->
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[220px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10">
            <div class="text-center p-6">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-amber-400/20 mx-auto mb-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">Meal preparation</p>
            </div>
            <!-- <img src="/images/community/feeding-prep.jpg" alt="Preparing meals" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> -->
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[220px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10">
            <div class="text-center p-6">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-amber-400/20 mx-auto mb-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">Children receiving meals</p>
            </div>
            <!-- <img src="/images/community/feeding-children.jpg" alt="Children receiving meals" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> -->
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 min-h-[220px] flex items-center justify-center border border-amber-400/10 sm:col-span-2">
            <div class="text-center p-6">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-amber-400/20 mx-auto mb-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15.75l5.159-5.159a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l5.159 5.159m-1.5-1.5l1.409-1.409a2.25 2.25 0 013.182 0l2.909 2.909M3.75 21h16.5M13.5 12h.008v.008H13.5V12z"/>
              </svg>
              <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">The community together</p>
            </div>
            <!-- <img src="/images/community/feeding-community.jpg" alt="The community together" class="w-full h-full object-cover"> -->
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
 
      <!-- Video section -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="section-heading text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-white mb-8">
          Watch the <span class="text-amber-400">Story</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-amber-400/5 border border-amber-400/10 min-h-[280px] sm:min-h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center p-8">
            <svg class="w-14 h-14 text-amber-400/20 mx-auto mb-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0116 0z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.91 11.672a.375.375 0 010 .656l-5.603 3.113a.375.375 0 01-.557-.328V8.887c0-.286.307-.466.557-.327l5.603 3.112z"/>
            </svg>
            <p class="font-body text-amber-400/40 text-sm mb-2">Video coming soon</p>
            <p class="font-body text-amber-400/25 text-xs">Replace with Facebook or YouTube embed</p>
          </div>
          <!--
            Facebook embed:
            <iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=YOUR_VIDEO_URL"
              class="w-full min-h-[400px]" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
 
            YouTube embed:
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YOUR_VIDEO_ID"
              class="w-full min-h-[400px]" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          -->
        </div>
      </div>
 
      <!-- Quote -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-400/10 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-400/5 to-transparent p-8 sm:p-10 mb-16">
        <p class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-amber-400/80 italic leading-relaxed mb-4">
          "A business that takes from a community without giving back is no business at all."
        </p>
        <p class="font-body text-gray-500 text-sm">— eKoneni Lounge</p>
      </div>
 
      <!-- Navigation footer -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 pt-8 border-t border-amber-400/10">
        <a href="/community" class="btn-outline px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full font-body text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18"/>
          </svg>
          All Stories
        </a>
        <a href="/community/house-rebuild" class="font-body text-amber-400 text-sm inline-flex items-center gap-2 hover:gap-3 transition-all duration-200">
          Next story: A Family Lost Everything
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
 
    </div>
  </section>
 
</MainLayout>
